    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "TO : A. H. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FROM :",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "SUBJECT: MISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "PURPOSE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "To recommend that Bureau liaison contact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "OSI to determine whether photographs allegedly taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "by the captioned individual of a flying disc in 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "were furnished by OSI to the office of Drew Pearson.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "BACKGROUND",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Bureau files reflect that on August 29, 1947,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "a [REDACTED], called at the Phoenix Office",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "exhibiting credentials reflecting he represented A-2,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Fourth Air Force, Hamilton Field, California. He asked an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Agent to accompany him to interview [REDACTED] who",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "previously reported the photographing of a flying disc in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Phoenix on the afternoon of July 7, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "The Phoenix Office contacted SAC Harry Kimball of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "the San Francisco Office and Mr. Kimball verified the fact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "that [REDACTED] come to Phoenix as a representative of Colonel",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] of Hamilton Field, and it was suggested the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Phoenix Office assist [REDACTED] not in investigating the matter",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "but in simply talking with Dr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "By letter dated September 4, 1947, the Phoenix",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Office set forth in four pages the results of this interview",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "and stated [REDACTED] had requested the negatives from [REDACTED] who",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "did not have them in his immediate possession. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "stated, however, he would deliver them to the FBI the following",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "morning for transmittal to [REDACTED] at Hamilton Field, California.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "On the morning of August 30, 1947, [REDACTED] delivered",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "the negatives to the Phoenix Office at which time they were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "accepted with the understanding they were being given to Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "[REDACTED], a representative of the Army Air Force Intelligence,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "United States Army, and that there was little, if any, chance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "of his getting the negatives back. Mr. [REDACTED] turned the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "negatives over to the FBI with the full understanding they were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "being given to the Air Force and he would not get them back.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "(62-85894-80, page 4)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
